  "detailed_description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4256270/extras/9570afeb3887624b86b47bca8f31b71e.poster.avif?t=1774138005\" width=594 height=334 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4256270/extras/9570afeb3887624b86b47bca8f31b71e.webm?t=1774138005\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4256270/extras/9570afeb3887624b86b47bca8f31b71e.mp4?t=1774138005\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Rhythm action meets martial arts in an unprecedented journey to Deukdo (Enlightenment).</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Achieve inner awakening and crush enemies from all directions (四方八方) with perfect timing!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Are you prepared to reach the state of Deukdo?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4256270/extras/c21f5dfa2a771d791c017adccf06ce99.poster.avif?t=1774138005\" width=594 height=334 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4256270/extras/c21f5dfa2a771d791c017adccf06ce99.webm?t=1774138005\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4256270/extras/c21f5dfa2a771d791c017adccf06ce99.mp4?t=1774138005\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Master the beat with only WASD, diagonal keys, and your innate sense of rhythm.</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >True mastery is achieved with both hands.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4256270/extras/b4fea3529a6771aa8798a311eeec8ac9.poster.avif?t=1774138005\" width=594 height=334 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4256270/extras/b4fea3529a6771aa8798a311eeec8ac9.webm?t=1774138005\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4256270/extras/b4fea3529a6771aa8798a311eeec8ac9.mp4?t=1774138005\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>The evil spirits themselves are the melody.</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Unpredictable rhythms that shift between calm and chaos, and irregular attacks weaving through various instruments, will constantly test your composure.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4256270/extras/01bd94c7556346e816afac5f210e4b23.poster.avif?t=1774138005\" width=594 height=334 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4256270/extras/01bd94c7556346e816afac5f210e4b23.webm?t=1774138005\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4256270/extras/01bd94c7556346e816afac5f210e4b23.mp4?t=1774138005\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Experience a world of brutal beauty.</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >From the tranquil temple courtyard to the source of evil.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Trace your Master's footsteps through diverse oriental landscapes.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Meditate with the mystical prayer beads found on your journey to leap into unknown dimensions.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>The Journey Awaits...</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Immersive Narrative:</strong> A monk's quest to restore the balance of Yin and Yang.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>8 Main Stages</strong>: A perilous pilgrimage to the source of evil, leading to Transcendental battles within Nirvana.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>3 Prayer Bead Realms:</strong> Hidden dimensions beyond time and space, featuring entirely new melodies.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>19-Track OST:</strong> Heart-pounding Oriental beats.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Merciful Practice Mode:</strong> Fear not failure.</p></li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4256270/extras/a0c7129d312481ff687792f9cc8fb3bb.poster.avif?t=1774138005\" width=594 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4256270/extras/a0c7129d312481ff687792f9cc8fb3bb.webm?t=1774138005\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4256270/extras/a0c7129d312481ff687792f9cc8fb3bb.mp4?t=1774138005\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span> </h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>--------------------------------------------------</strong><br><strong>The puppy is crying while playing the Kkwaenggwari (Gong)!</strong><br><br><br><strong>It seems only a 'Wishlist' can comfort him.</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4256270/extras/318cea4cddc86717789caf47d08fbde0.poster.avif?t=1774138005\" width=478 height=396 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4256270/extras/318cea4cddc86717789caf47d08fbde0.webm?t=1774138005\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4256270/extras/318cea4cddc86717789caf47d08fbde0.mp4?t=1774138005\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Join our official Discord to hear pre-released tracks and get the latest dev updates!</strong><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4256270/extras/f3c00469e159a363714f147373844eff.avif?t=1774138005\" width=209 height=218 /></span></h2>",
